      "body" : "@Shervin you can. exactly as you wrote. <a href=\"http://docs.spring.io/spring/docs/current/spring-framework-reference/htmlsingle/#beans-scanning-autodetection\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">&quot;Alternatively, you can specify a comma-separated list that includes the parent package of each class.&quot;</a> (also see the expected answer)"
