    "creation_date" : 1299823411,
    "answer_id" : 5269527,
    "question_id" : 5269450,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can add multiple base packages (see <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/5269450/multiple-packages-in-contextcomponent-scan-spring-config/5271220#5271220\">axtavt's answer</a>), but you can also <a href=\"http://static.springsource.org/spring/docs/3.0.x/spring-framework-reference/html/beans.html#beans-scanning-filters\" rel=\"noreferrer\">filter what's scanned</a> inside the base package:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;context:component-scan base-package=\"x.y.z\"&gt;\n   &lt;context:include-filter type=\"regex\" expression=\"(service|controller)\\..*\"/&gt;\n&lt;/context:component-scan&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
        "account_id" : 40774,
