      "creation_date" : 1445968784,
      "post_id" : 5271220,
      "comment_id" : 54544568,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "This answer implies that there is NOT recursion for the members of base-package BUT there IS:   <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/7774295/spring-xml-file-configuration-hierarchy-help-explanation/7774597#7774597\" title=\"spring xml file configuration hierarchy help explanation\">stackoverflow.com/questions/7774295/&hellip;</a>  .  I would suggest altering the answer a little to make this clear."
    } ],
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 36208,
      "reputation" : 243304,
      "user_id" : 103154,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/2a48823f3303f6c34f30574b9cb68e48?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "axtavt",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/103154/axtavt"
    },
    "is_accepted" : true,
    "score" : 295,
    "last_activity_date" : 1299836242,
    "creation_date" : 1299836242,
    "answer_id" : 5271220,
    "question_id" : 5269450,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>The following approach is correct:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;context:component-scan base-package=\"x.y.z.service, x.y.z.controller\" /&gt; \n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Note that the error complains about <code>x.y.z.dao.daoservice.LoginDAO</code>, which is not in the packages mentioned above, perhaps you forgot to add it:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;context:component-scan base-package=\"x.y.z.service, x.y.z.controller, x.y.z.dao\" /&gt; \n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
