    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 2,
    "last_activity_date" : 1481863548,
    "creation_date" : 1481863548,
    "answer_id" : 41177417,
    "question_id" : 5269450,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If x.y.z is the common package then you can use:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;context:component-scan base-package=\"x.y.z.*\"&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>it will include all the package that is start with x.y.z like:\nx.y.z.controller,x.y.z.service etc.</p>\n"
