    "question_id" : 5269450,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>For Example you have the package \"com.abc\" and you have multiple packages inside it, You can use like</p>\n\n<pre><code>@ComponentScan(\"com.abc\")\n</code></pre>\n"
