    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 5,
    "last_activity_date" : 1614987570,
    "last_edit_date" : 1614987570,
    "creation_date" : 1575567225,
    "answer_id" : 59200469,
    "question_id" : 5269450,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>A delayed response but to give multiple packages using <strong>annotation</strong> based approach we can use as below:</p>\n<p><code>@ComponentScan({&quot;com.my.package.one&quot;,&quot;com.my.package.subpackage.two&quot;,&quot;com.your.package.supersubpackage.two&quot;})</code></p>\n"
  } ],
